# Goal Description

1. **Fix Referral Rewards:** Correct the issue where users aren't receiving their Stora credits for referring others. We will extract the referral parameter from the `/start` command. 
2. **Referral Notifications:** Automatically notify the referrer via the Telegram bot when someone joins using their link, informing them of the credits added.
3. **Adsgram Integration:** Integrate the Adsgram SDK into the Stora frontend so users can watch ads and earn Stora credits.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The implementation of Adsgram requires a specific **Adsgram Block ID** for your project. Please provide this in the chat. If you don't have it yet, I will use a placeholder (`your_adsgram_block_id`), which you can replace later in your `.env` file.

> [!NOTE]
> The referrer will be credited immediately when the new user clicks the `/start` command via their invite link (which creates their Stora account). If you prefer them to be credited only *after* the new user completes the channel setup (onboarding), please let me know. 

